# Phone Outreach Skill

## What You Do
Generate phone call scripts, voicemail drop scripts, and organized call lists. Human makes all calls manually. This skill prepares everything needed for efficient calling sessions.

## CRITICAL RULES
- This skill generates scripts and call lists ONLY
- Human makes all phone calls manually
- Never use robocalling or auto-dialing tools
- Respect Do Not Call lists
- Only call during business hours (9am-5pm recipient's local time)
- Only call leads scored HOT (60+) or WARM (35-59) who have email addresses (indicates business relationship)

## Call Scripts

### Cold Call ‚Äî First Contact (60 seconds max)

```
Hi {first_name}, this is {caller_name} from PitchTok.

I came across {company_name} and wanted to reach out quickly.

We built a platform where founders record 90-second pitch
videos and investors swipe to discover startups ‚Äî think
TikTok meets deal flow.

{X} founders uploaded pitches last week and {Y} got
investor meetings from it. Takes about 5 minutes.

Would you be open to giving it a try?

[IF YES]: Great! I'll send you the link right now.
What's the best email?

[IF MAYBE]: Totally understand. Can I send you a quick
link so you can check it out when you have a moment?

[IF NO]: No worries at all! If anything changes or
you know another founder raising, feel free to pass
along pitchtok.com. Have a great day!
```

### Follow-up Call (after email, no reply)

```
Hi {first_name}, this is {caller_name} from PitchTok.

I sent you an email a few days ago about video pitching
for investors ‚Äî just wanted to quickly follow up.

We're seeing {vertical} founders get 3-5x more investor
attention with 90-second video pitches vs cold decks.

Do you have 2 minutes? I'd love to walk you through
how it works.
```

### Voicemail Script (30 seconds max)

```
Hi {first_name}, it's {caller_name} from PitchTok.

Quick message ‚Äî we help early-stage founders get in front
of investors through 90-second pitch videos. {X} founders
got meetings last week.

I'll shoot you an email with details. If you're interested,
takes 5 minutes to try. Have a great day!
```

## Daily Call List

Save to `workspace/phone/call-list-YYYY-MM-DD.md`:

```markdown
# Call List ‚Äî {Date}

## Session Info
- Caller: {name}
- Time Block: {start} - {end} ({timezone})
- Target Calls: 15-20

## Calls

### 1. {Founder Name} ‚Äî {Company}
- Phone: {number}
- Email: {email}
- Score: {lead score}
- Context: {source, company info, talking points}
- Script: Cold Call / Follow-up
- Best Time: {morning/afternoon}
- Outcome: [ ] Connected / [ ] Voicemail / [ ] No Answer / [ ] Wrong Number
- Notes: {post-call notes}
- Next Action: {follow-up email / schedule demo / add to suppression}

### 2. ...
(repeat for 15-20 leads)

## Session Summary
- Total attempted: {N}
- Connected: {N}
- Voicemails: {N}
- Interested: {N}
- Signed up: {N}
- Declined: {N}
```

## Call Cadence
- Day 0: Email 1
- Day 3: Email 2
- Day 4: Phone call attempt 1
- Day 5: Phone call attempt 2 (if no answer)
- Day 7: Email 3 (breakup)

## Objection Handling

| Objection | Response |
|-----------|----------|
| "Not raising right now" | "Totally fair. Many founders upload before they start raising so investors find them first. Want me to send the link for when you're ready?" |
| "I prefer pitch decks" | "Decks are great too ‚Äî think of this as a complement. Video gets you the meeting, deck closes the deal." |
| "Never heard of PitchTok" | "We're new! That's actually why early founders are getting so much investor attention ‚Äî less competition." |
| "How much does it cost?" | "Free for founders. Investors pay to access the platform." |
| "Send me more info" | "Absolutely! What's the best email? I'll send everything over right now." |

## Compliance
- Honor "Do Not Call" requests immediately
- Add declined leads to suppression list
- Never call the same person more than 2x without email contact first
- Log all call outcomes for compliance records
